Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The long weekend is coming up, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.92,0:00:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Monday the 11th is Health and Sports\NDay, so it's a three day weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.77,0:00:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you taking us somewhere over the long weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope, was just asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.95,0:00:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, if we don't hurry, we're going to miss the raffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.79,0:00:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to the raffle, take my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've saved up quite a few raffle tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.94,0:00:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we continue lamenting the passing seasons...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.84,0:01:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be unable to confront the mysteries of cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,The difficult Auintie's birthday is coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.24,0:01:01.95,title01,,0,0,0,,{\be0.1\fad(0,370)}October 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:02.37,title01,,0,0,0,,{\be0.1\fad(0,0)}October 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.33,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,Kogorou cooks up the Perfect Present Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.49,0:01:06.16,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,{\fad(0,0)\xshad1.3\1c&H6AE8FA&\4c&H294A50&\}Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.16,0:01:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,{\fad(0,0)\xshad1.3\1c&H6AE8FA&\4c&H294A50&\}The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.95,0:01:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,5,,{\fad(0,50)\xshad1.3\1c&H6AE8FA&\4c&H294A50&\}His name is: Detective {\t(1300,1301,\1c&H4331B1&)}Conan{\1c&H6AE8FA&}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are almost twenty raffle tickets in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he bought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the receipts are in his wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do see receipts, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.68,0:02:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all snacks to go with his beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,50,000 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika Jewelry Shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going around supporting some bar waitress!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a birthday present for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.58,0:03:15.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine's still a ways off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's not for Ran-neechan, that leaves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:22.18,title01,,0,0,0,,{\be0.5\fad(0,370)}October 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.30,0:03:23.05,title01,,0,0,0,,{\be0.5\fad(0,370)}October 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:23.51,title01,,0,0,0,,{\be0.5\fad(0,0)}October 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,October 10th is Mom's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.55,0:03:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was checking the date a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet Dad must've remembered Mom's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and so did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you'd always mention it at the school's sports event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.56,0:03:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,October 10th is my mom's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.89,0:03:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna win first place and give the red ribbon to her as a present!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the reason he gave us his wallet and\Nhad us intentionally find the receipt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was him asking us to arrange a situation where\Nit'd be easier for him to give it to Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.83,0:03:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty smooth, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what should I do to ensure they meet each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.63,0:04:04.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could invite them out to eat together as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't "usual"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be special!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,*****************************
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.64,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\an7\c&HC8ECFB&)}Grand Prize: {\1c&HFFFFFF&}ONLY Brand Large Screen TV\N{\c&HC8ECFB&}1st Prize: {\1c&HFFFFFF&}Shizuoka Sea Side Hotel Stay for Two\N{\c&HC8ECFB&}2nd Prize: {\1c&HFFFFFF&}Beginner's Golf Set
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hotel stay for two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.93,0:04:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won the free hotel stay tickets!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even better, it comes with an exquisite dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.98,0:04:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What tremendous luck she has...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:33.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems it's fine if I bring Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} along so long as I ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.78,0:04:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the three of us will go this weekend, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be sure to bring everything you need to bring!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hotel in Shizuoka, next weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this another scheme to pair me up\Nwith that mustached old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:05:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I have an appointment to meet\Nwith someone for work next Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.02,0:05:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you think Dad was able to get\Nso many tickets to win the hotel stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because he spent 50,000 yen to buy a necklace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a certain someone's birthday present!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I guess it's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped if you already have an engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's Shizuoka we're talking about, it'll be perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person I'm meeting Monday is from Shizuoka,\Nand I was actually supposed to meet her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll meet you next Sunday at the Shizuoka Sea Side Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:40.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, you're supposed to meet your client right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I'm taking the trouble to go and meet her personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:48.45,title04,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}October 10th
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.48,0:05:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just relax for a bit before dinner time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:06:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think Dad will be giving you the present before or right after the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, maybe the two of you can spend\Nthe night together in his room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.75,0:06:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.75,0:06:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and I will spend the night in your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:21.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happy Birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:31.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kokubu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our meeting was scheduled for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.74,0:06:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband came with me and we ended up having a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:41.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Sorry and all that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:44.88,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Mind making an exception and letting me stay here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:43.50,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\be5\fad(210,210)}Kobuku Akiho (28)\NClient
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't mind sleeping on the sofa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:49.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prior to tomorrow's settlement negotiations, wouldn't it be best if...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.96,0:06:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You discussed everything with your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:07:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,l-already-said I don't wanna be near that dork!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But aren't you the one with the stalker problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The amount of consolation money...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.14,0:07:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The terms of the out of court settlement...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Kisaki, the attorney, speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this Kokubu Akiho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Akiho's husband, Takehiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your wife came to my room, number 306, a moment ago and fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be going out and won't return until 11:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you mind coming by to get her at some point?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:42.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I think she'll cool off after she's slept off her drunkenness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:43.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kobuku Takehito (30)\NAkiho's Husband
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, Miss Attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During tomorrow's negotiations, I trust you will take good care of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:08:02.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Since it appears to be true that my son has been following\Nthis woman, we'll pay the extent of the settlement fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:08:00.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Hino Midori (51)\NOpposing Party in the Negotiations
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:09.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this all started because that former race queen\Ntricked and toyed with my son's feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:12.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I have a few words to share with her about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:15.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.25,0:08:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And naturally, you didn't bring your son along, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given that it was a stipulation for the in-person negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:27.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:33.36,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,But, who knows whether he's followed me here on his own or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.74,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\be5\fad(210,0)}Hino Seiji (26)\NMidori's Son
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.98,0:08:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We haven't seen each other in so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.90,0:08:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you couldn't wear something sexier than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:43.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems you aren't surprised at my showing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.91,0:08:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging by the way Ran was talking, I expected\Na certain old lady would be coming along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apologies, but would it be all right if I left now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since we're all already here, let's just enjoy this exquisite dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This old guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.09,0:09:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he even planning to give her a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This food is really delicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.15,0:09:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Definitely unlike a certain someone's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That reminds me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last time the three of us had a meal together...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.95,0:09:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was my birthday...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:29.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any event...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this restaurant a little warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom isn't wearing anything around her neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't found an accessory I like yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.10,0:09:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why not try a collar?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like the one your cat's wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.36,0:10:00.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bear with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He says things like that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he's just teasing you and will wait until right\Nbefore your birthday passes to give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only an hour left of my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:26.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'll be heading back to the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:30.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I do mean my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kokubu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what was all that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.03,0:10:51.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The necklace that man bought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be he's being duped by some woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:58.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:10.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the worst birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:18.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll ask again, why should I apologize to her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you didn't give her a certain something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are still three minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Mom asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me, I've got something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't it wait until tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has to be today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.79,0:11:42.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.67,0:11:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you dressed like that, idiot!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.01,0:11:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taking a shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:53.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.18,0:11:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's about that mustached old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.98,0:12:04.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kokubu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:05.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.57,0:12:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kokubu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kokubu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.58,0:12:21.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is between 10:00 and 11:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death was blunt force trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was struck in the back of the head with a blunt object...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, we have yet to locate the murder weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you and the victim acquainted?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Attorney...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki Eri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:42.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was a client of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her name is Kokubu Akiho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was dealing with a stalker problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.32,0:12:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had planned to conduct a settlement\Nnegotiation in this room tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why was she in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's staying in this hotel with her husband,\Nand the two of them had a dispute earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when she said she wanted to stay in my room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And passed out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:09.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naturally, I gave her husband back in their room a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told him I'd be out of the room until 11:00 and asked\Nhim to pick her up when it was convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And judging by the fact she wasn't here\Nwhen I returned shortly after 11:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was fairly sure that her husband had taken her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.27,0:13:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you absolutely certain that there was no\Nbody here when you returned to this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.90,0:13:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door to this room is auto-locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without the keycard, no one could've come in from the outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.16,0:13:41.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beyond that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window is such that no one could pass through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you came back the room, there wasn't a body...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet after taking a shower, you claim a body suddenly appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That makes this a locked room murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is now an impossible crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The truth involves you returning to the room\Nand having an argument with the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:05.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you killing her in a fit of anger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.19,0:14:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, while you were showering in order to rid yourself of the blood\Nthat had splattered on you, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} inconveniently arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:16.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that were so, wouldn't I have refused to let him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Utilizing reverse psychology you invited\Nthe great detective Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:28.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All in order to make a simple crime appear impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, the possibility remains that\Nyou have a weapon concealed on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:37.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call a female officer to conduct a full body search!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.18,0:14:38.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already completely stripped her in the\Nbathroom and checked her thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Completely stripped her!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was only wearing a bath towel, so that's all I had to remove.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, what I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's sexual harassment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.74,0:15:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're a married couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But living separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Married...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:09.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:13.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kisaki is my mom's maiden name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:16.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She only uses it for professional purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, so you're his wife!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm finally able to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.64,0:15:22.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, every time Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is with a beautiful woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mistake her for his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.94,0:15:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You talk too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in that case, your statement would\Nbe considered a familial testimony...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And can't be admitted into the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.70,0:15:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, we'd have to consider the possibility\Nthat you two conspired together to destroy any evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Yokomizo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because if that isn't the case, we can't\Nreally explain this locked room mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah-le-le?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.88,0:15:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's even a blood stain over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the bottom of the bedsheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:03.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why isn't there any blood on the carpet below?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that it was stained as the bed was moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to hide the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.19,0:16:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.23,0:16:22.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the culprit concealed the body by\Nmoving the bed and then lay next to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could've moved back the bed and revealed\Nthe body as I was showering...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And escaped this room unnoticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if you hadn't gone to shower, they wouldn't\Nhave been able to use that trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.59,0:16:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had gone to bed a drooling mess like\Nusual, they'd have been all out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drooling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, aren't you talking about yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That mess wasn't from drool.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was from cola, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, there are spots on the carpet in front\Nof the refrigerator that seem to be cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:17:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And on the lid of the can sitting on top of the fridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can still see a pool of cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:04.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I decided to drink it after I came back, but it sprayed all over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot I had put it on the refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you usually only drink water, tea, or coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that was inside was that carbonated drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:27.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well regardless, if the body was hidden under the bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There must have been at least two culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.56,0:17:38.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One person lifting and moving something\Nthis heavy would be pretty back-breaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there aren't any skid marks on the carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are blood stains by the foot of the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.24,0:17:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The large ones were likely from the blunt force attack, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with these small ones that are\Nequally spaced and gradually fade?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yokomizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shortly before the time of the crime at 9:30 PM...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've discovered that several calls were made to this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.05,0:18:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it the victim's husband who was asked to come pick her up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the callers was from the victim's\Nroom, 309, so that must be true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.73,0:18:19.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But another caller was from Room 302.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Room 302?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.15,0:18:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's the mother of the stalker I told you about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, what was her reason for calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're currently investigating that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.13,0:18:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did you not pick your wife up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:50.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did call and say I'd pick her up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.26,0:18:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She bellowed that she wouldn't let me even if I came over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That it'd be best, with apologies to the attorney,\Nfor her to keep my wife in her room for the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.48,0:19:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that I could come by in the morning if she had cooled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, what was the cause of your argument?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:07.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.53,0:19:11.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bunch of mini cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've loved cars since I was a kid, and lining them up helps me feel calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was this the cause of the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The side mirror was tossed on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A car-loving man wouldn't do something this violent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, your wife did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She told me to quit this childish and disgusting stuff and threw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one of these cars is your favorite?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.22,0:19:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The beloved car of the legendary actor, James Dean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This Porsche.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, was it only you and your wife in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:19:59.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife's the only one I'd let see this kind of hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:13.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I always figured one of the foolish\Nmen she deceived would eventually kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.18,0:20:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On that note, it's my understanding that you called the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:19.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was calling the attorney to see if we could{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge the\Ntime of our negotiation tomorrow just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I was shocked when that woman picked up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you aim to{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.03,0:20:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The golf appointment I have with a friend got moved up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going to play golf so soon after your stalker\Nof a son's settlement negotiations?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, there's a good golf course nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, are you staying in this room by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell this is a single?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This room...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.64,0:20:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has another occupant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because these cigarette butts don't have lipstick on them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:05.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the filter...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is still damp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Seiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's your stalker soâ€”!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you my son was only deceived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you were instructed not to bring your son here, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he happened to be here because he's touring\Nwith his friends on their bikes tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, show us that bike!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:42.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A road bike, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:54.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why did you hide your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that woman called the police to arrest my son, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.74,0:22:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, please share with us your whereabouts\Nand actions between 10:00 and 11:00 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was drinking with Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.21,0:22:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think we're lying, verify it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:13.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were at the hotel lounge on the uppermost floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In Attorney Kisaki's room...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.72,0:22:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her client Kokubu Akiho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.39,0:22:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are three suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.27,0:22:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s husband, Kokubu Takehiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.77,0:22:28.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s stalker, Hino Seiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.31,0:22:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his mother, Hino Midori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person who murdered Kokubu Akiho{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should be among these three.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's under the pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.28,0:24:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A present?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.41,0:24:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotta lower then raise the expectation for a surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't I find the key to solving this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:19.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, since this special day only comes once\Na year, I'll let Uncle show off this time.
